('c0000000-0005-0000-0000-000000000018', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'd0000000-0005-0000-0000-000000000003', 'AU-12', 'Audit Record Generation', 'Provide audit record generation capability for the events defined in AU-2 at system components.', 'detective', 'technical', 'high', 18),

