('c0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'd0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'GV.OC-01', 'The organizational context is understood', 'The circumstances -- mission, stakeholder expectations, dependencies, and legal, regulatory, and contractual requirements -- surrounding the organization''s cybersecurity risk management decisions are understood.', 'directive', 'management', 'high', 1),
