('c0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000006', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'd0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'GV.RM-01', 'Risk management objectives are established and agreed', 'Risk management objectives are established and expressed as statements that describe the intended cybersecurity state.', 'directive', 'management', 'high', 6),
