('c0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000008', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'd0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'GV.RR-01', 'Organizational leadership is responsible and accountable for cybersecurity risk', 'Organizational leadership takes responsibility and is held accountable for managing cybersecurity risk.', 'directive', 'management', 'critical', 8),
('c0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000009', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'd0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'GV.RR-02', 'Roles, responsibilities, and authorities for cybersecurity risk management are established', 'Cybersecurity roles, responsibilities, and authorities related to risk management are established and communicated.', 'directive', 'management', 'high', 9),
('c0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000010', 'f0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'd0000000-0006-0000-0000-000000000001', 'GV.PO-01', 'A policy for managing cybersecurity risks is established', 'A cybersecurity risk management policy based on organizational context, cybersecurity strategy, and priorities is established, communicated, and enforced.', 'directive', 'management', 'high', 10),
